Class TezOperator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.pig.impl.plan.Operator<TezOpPlanVisitor>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    NativeTezOper

    public class TezOperator
extends Operator<TezOpPlanVisitor>
    An operator model for a Tez job. Acts as a host to the plans that will execute in Tez vertices.
